name: Chuck the cactUSB.
description: This is Chuck, the newest member of the #cactusclan! His superpower is that he can store up to 8GB of data and keep them safely for you! He is limited to 100 pieces and comes boxed, numbered and with some added goodness already stored on him: his papertoy-self (exclusively on the stick) and a "ColorMeCactus"-sheet. Chuck is made of soft PVC and is using a Toshiba 8GB chip. He is 5cm tall and you don't need to feed or water him - just store some pics of water on him from time to time and he will stay happy! A couple of #cactusclan-stickers will also be added to the package for free. (markers not included.)

name: #cactusclan sticker pack
description: Set of 6 #cactusclan stickers - two of each colorway! more details and pics from all around the world here! Worldwide shipping included!

name: Chester
description: Meet Chester! This happy member of the Cactus Clan has just returned from a holiday in the lovely city of Arnsberg, where he met with fellow cacti and other folded creatures. Now he is well rested and ready for new adventures.. This papertoy measures approximately 11 cm when built. Just cut, fold & glue. Printed on thick paper. Each papertoy will be shipped with a little secret extra-goodie!

name: Gunther
description: This is Gunther! Another happy member of the Cactus Clan. He really is a nice and sweet guy, but don't get on his wrong foot or steal one of his bananas! don't get between an APEtus and his food.. but feed him some and he will be your best friend forever! This papertoy measures approximately 11 cm when built. Just cut, fold & glue. Printed on thick paper. Each papertoy will be shipped with a little secret extra-goodie!

name: K1X MechaBunny
description: exclusive and limited edition K1X custom of MechaBunny - designed and printed for the K1X Pop-Up Store in NYC. Each template is signed and numbered - only 12 were printed! - and comes with a signed moo-card. more info here: K1X MechaBunny
